name: Vintage pink check handmade bag
description:
You're sure to turn heads with this unusual shoulder bag made from vintage pink and maroon check knit fabric, with contrasting navy satin trim and a blue lining.

The bag has a lined main zip compartment with plenty of room to carry your purse, phone and other essentials securely. There’s also a front zip pocket perfect for keeping tickets and other small things safe. The durable navy strap clicks into place, is fully adjustable and can be worn over your shoulder or around your waist.

this handmade bag is a one-off – the one you see pictured is the one you’ll receive

Size: 15x20x5cm

More images: http://www.flickr.com/photos/suziesparkle/5202571008

name: Camouflage handmade bag
description:
Designed for urban survival, this practical shoulder bag is made from hard-wearing green and desert camouflage fabric. Eye-catching red trim and a red lining add a splash of colour.

The bag has a lined main zip compartment with plenty of room to carry your purse, phone and other essentials securely. There’s also a front zip pocket perfect for keeping tickets and other small things safe. The durable black strap clicks into place, is fully adjustable and can be worn over your shoulder or around your waist.

All of our handmade bags are one-offs – the bag you see pictured is the one you’ll receive.

Size: 15x20x5cm
